snippet.textDisplay: Dr christy thanks for the information you provid each and every day and I want to personally thank you for putting your life on the line and I don't want anything to happen to you and your family because I care about you and all the doctors and nurses out there and again I say thank you and stay strong God bless you and all the medical team 😊
